text: Mohanad Al-Shudukhi (; born 15 April 1999) is a Saudi professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Al-Bukayriyah on loan from Al-Raed. ==Career== Al-Shudukhi started his career with youth team Al-Raed on July 30, 2015 . where he was promoted from the youth team to the first team in 2018 .He played his first match against Al-Hilal on January 30, 2018 . ==References== == External links == * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Saudi Arabian footballers Category:Al-Raed FC players Category:Al-Bukayriyah FC players Category:Saudi Professional League players Category:Prince Mohammad bin Salman League players Category:Association football midfielders
